<H3> <TI>   U.S. Group Considers Purchases From Defense Enterprises </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    U.S. Group Considers Purchases From Defense Enterprises </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0350B Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 27 Apr 94 p 11 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0350B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
