<H3> <TI>   Business Leaders Request Representation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Business Leaders Request Representation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0651B Moscow OBSHCHAYA GAZETA in Russian No 16, 22-28 
Apr 94 p 7 </F>

<F P=103> 944F0651B </F>
