<H3> <TI>   Muscovites Polled on Daily Problems, Yeltsin's Presidency </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Muscovites Polled on Daily Problems, Yeltsin's Presidency </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0659A Moscow OBSHCHAYA GAZETA in Russian No 17, 29 Apr 
94 p 8 </F>

<F P=103> 944F0659A </F>
