<DATE1>   21 April 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100> RUSSIA </F>
<F P=101> POLITICAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Principles, Theses of `National Doctrine of Russia' Viewed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Principles, Theses of `National Doctrine of Russia' Viewed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P50139A Moscow MOSKOVSKAYA PRAVDA in Russian 21 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 94P50139A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow MOSKOVSKAYA PRAVDA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


