<H3> <TI>   New Limonov Book on Zhirinovskiy Excerpted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Limonov Book on Zhirinovskiy Excerpted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1193A Moscow ARGUMENTY I FAKTY in Russian No 18, May 94 
p 3 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1193A </F>
