<H3> <TI>   Commission on Commodities Exchanges Urges Tax Cuts </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Commission on Commodities Exchanges Urges Tax Cuts </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0799A Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 30 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
