<H3> <TI>   Entrepreneurs, Businessmen Protest Against Taxation System </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Entrepreneurs, Businessmen Protest Against Taxation System </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0809A Moscow NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA in Russian 30 Apr 94 p 6 </F>
