<H3> <TI>   Chubays on Measures for Check Privatization in Regions </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Chubays on Measures for Check Privatization in Regions </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0790A Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 23 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
