<H3> <TI>   Railway Economic Program Highlighted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Railway Economic Program Highlighted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0803A Moscow ZHELEZNODOROZHNYY TRANSPORT in Russian No 
1, Jan 94 pp 2-4 </F>

<F P=103> 944E0803A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ZHELEZNODOROZHNYY TRANSPORT </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


