<H3> <TI>   Economic Situation for First Quarter 1994 </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Economic Situation for First Quarter 1994 </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944E0787A Moscow EKONOMIKA I ZHIZN in Russian No 16, Apr 94 
pp 1,4 </F>

<F P=103> 944E0787A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow EKONOMIKA I ZHIZN </F>
