  By 28 March of this year agricultural enterprises sold 
through all distribution channels 17,500 tonnes of greenhouse 
vegetables (24,200 tonnes in 1993). Of this, 12,800 tonnes (73 
percent of the total volume) were sold to procurement 
organizations, which is one-third less than last year: 


