percent); and 836.5 km of gas pipes (94 percent). 
  Construction organizations of all forms of ownership on the 
territory of the Russian Federation performed R8.5 trillion 
worth of contract work in January-March of this year, which is 
24 percent less than over the corresponding period of last year. 
