<H3> <TI>   Kuchma-Hrynyov Bloc Seen Likely To Split </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kuchma-Hrynyov Bloc Seen Likely To Split </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1182A Lvov POST-POSTUP in Ukrainian No 12, 22-28 Apr 94 
p A3 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1182A </F>
<F P=104>  Lvov POST-POSTUP </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


