<H3> <TI>   Harmful Pesticides Being Employed by Agricultural Sector </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Harmful Pesticides Being Employed by Agricultural Sector </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1188B Kiev ZELENYY SVIT in Ukrainian No 5, Apr 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1188B </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev ZELENYY SVIT </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
