<H3> <TI>   Growth In 1993 Direct Investments </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Growth In 1993 Direct Investments </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1106D Tallinn RAHVA HaaL in Estonian 11 Mar 94 
p </F>



