<H3> <TI>   Poll Rates Preelection Standing of Political Parties </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Poll Rates Preelection Standing of Political Parties </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1206A Riga NEATKARIGA CINA in Latvian 16 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
